Demo
====


Continuous Inspection:

1. Show users in the system
2. Show email notification every user can set
3. Show dashboard for each user
4. Switch to developer user and go into violations drilldown
5. Comment one violation and assign it to another developer who is responsible for it
6. Login as the other developer an view the newly assigned review
7. Comment the violation
8. Show manual violation feature by commenting a strange looking line of code
9. Create action plan and show howto change a dashboard


General Hints:

- Show usage of clouds
- Show usage of lcom4 metric